---
/* About section component */
---
<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="about section">

  <!-- Section Title -->
  <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <div><span>Learn More</span> <span class="description-title">About Us</span></div>
  </div>
  <!-- End Section Title -->

  <div class="container">

    <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center">
      
      <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="about-image position-relative">
          <img src="assets/img/about/space-hero.png"
               class="img-fluid rounded-4 shadow-sm"
               alt="Green Orbit Space hero image"
               loading="lazy">
          <div class="experience-badge">
            <span class="years">15+</span>
            <span class="text">Years Experience</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6 mt-4 mt-lg-0" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Translating Missions into Meaningful Stories</h2>
        <p>
          Green Orbit Space is a strategic communications and PR agency dedicated to the space sector. We partner with organisations, startups, and ventures to:
          <ul>
            <li>Communicate complex missions and sustainability initiatives with clarity and impact</li>
            <li>Develop strategic narratives, campaigns, and engagement frameworks that resonate globally</li>
            <li>Foster collaboration, innovation, and responsible storytelling to drive sector-wide trust and credibility</li>
          </ul>
          Our approach combines insight, strategy, and creative storytelling to ensure every project, partnership, and initiative is both meaningful and influential.
        </p>

<div class="row g-4 mt-3">
  
          <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="400">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
              <h5>Communications Expertise</h5>
              <p>
                Our team bridges communications, PR, and strategy to help space organisations craft narratives that inspire, educate, and engage audiences worldwide.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="450">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <i class="bi bi-lightbulb-fill"></i>
              <h5>Impactful Storytelling</h5>
              <p>
                We transform technical missions and complex initiatives into compelling stories that highlight impact, sustainability, and innovation for global audiences.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

</div>

          <a href="work.html" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">View Work</a>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div class="testimonial-section mt-5 pt-5" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      <div class="row">

        <div class="col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="testimonial-intro">
            <h3>What People Say</h3>
            <p>
              Colleagues and collaborators across the space, sustainability, and digital sectors share how our work together has shaped their progress.
            </p>
            <div class="swiper-nav-buttons mt-4">
              <button class="slider-prev"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i></button>
              <button class="slider-next"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="testimonial-slider swiper init-swiper">
            <script type="application/json" class="swiper-config">
              {
                "loop": true,
                "speed": 800,
                "autoplay": { "delay": 5000 },
                "slidesPerView": 1,
                "spaceBetween": 30,
                "navigation": {
                  "nextEl": ".slider-next",
                  "prevEl": ".slider-prev"
                },
                "breakpoints": {
                  "768": {
                    "slidesPerView": 2
                  }
                }
              }
            </script>

            <div class="swiper-wrapper">

              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                  <div class="rating mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    "Ryan brings clarity and strategic insight to every challenge. His leadership in sustainability and space policy has been indispensable to our work."
                  </p>
                  <div class="client-info d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
                    <img src="assets/img/person/person-f-1.webp" class="client-img" alt="Client" loading="lazy">
                    <div>
                      <h6 class="mb-0">Eleanor Vance</h6>
                      <span>Industry Lead</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                  <div class="rating mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-half"></i>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    "His ability to translate complex technical topics into clear narratives is remarkable. A valuable partner in shaping communications strategy."
                  </p>
                  <div class="client-info d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
                    <img src="assets/img/person/person-m-1.webp" class="client-img" alt="Client" loading="lazy">
                    <div>
                      <h6 class="mb-0">David Kim</h6>
                      <span>Communications Director</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                  <div class="rating mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    "Ryanâ€™s systems thinking and structured methodology helped us build an evidence-led sustainability framework we now use across programmes."
                  </p>
                  <div class="client-info d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
                    <img src="assets/img/person/person-f-2.webp" class="client-img" alt="Client" loading="lazy">
                    <div>
                      <h6 class="mb-0">Isabella Diaz</h6>
                      <span>Sustainability Analyst</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                  <div class="rating mb-3">
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                    <i class="bi bi-star-half"></i>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    "His depth of knowledge across space, digital, and sustainability makes him uniquely capable of bridging sectors and driving aligned progress."
                  </p>
                  <div class="client-info d-flex align-items-center mt-4">
                    <img src="assets/img/person/person-f-3.webp" class="client-img" alt="Client" loading="lazy">
                    <div>
                      <h6 class="mb-0">Olivia Chen</h6>
                      <span>Strategy Lead</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>
